rem Quantum Lab
rem 8/23/2017

items quantum ram
items reality simulator

do Examine Lab
 [
  setflag seen qlab
  ifflag simulator off
   [
    print The alarm rings through the room, and the scientist is dead. Plugged into
    print the reality simulator through a cyberjack at the base of his skull, his brain
    ifflag have ram
     [
      print was short circuited when you unplugged the machine.
     |
      print was short circuited when you unplugged the machine. The ram you're looking for
      print is now accessible.
     ]
   |
    print The alarm rings throughout the room, but there's a scientist in the back that 
    print pays it no mind. He's plugged into a VR Sim using a cyberjack at the base of 
    print his skull. In the back of the room sits the ram you're looking for, operating 
    print the reality simulator.
   ]
 ]

ifflag seen qlab
 [
  do Examine Scientist
   ifflag simulator off
    [
     print The scientist came to an end quickly. When you shut off the simulator, it
     print short-circuited his brain. All his neurons blowing out at once.    
    |
     print The scientist sits in the back of the room plugged into a reality simulator.
     print With the simulator plugged into the base of his skull, he twitches now and
     print then responding to the input from the machine.
    ]
 |]

do Exit Lab
 [
  ifflag have ram
   [
    ifflag planted chip
     [
      print Finally finished, you leave the lab.
      go Hosaka North
     |
      ifflag know holografixs
       [
        print You need to plant the chip for The Finn while you're here.
       |
        print You need to plant the chip for the owner while you're here.
       ]
     ]
   |
    print Not without the ram.
   ]
 ]


